{"id": "fsa5t6", "title": "A wild death cross just appeared; analysis of the last 10 SPX death crosses", "selftext": "TL;DR: death cross has ***preceded*** a major plunge (>-15%) only 3 out of the last 10 times (though this includes 2001 and 2008); death cross has preceded a deeper bottom or retest of the lows 4 out of the last 10 times; death cross has indicated a bottom 3 out of the last 10 times.\n\n&#x200B;\n\nThe new buzz word you'll see spammed in every daily thread by the bears is now \"a death cross has just formed\". A death cross is basically the cross between the 50-day moving average (blue lines) below the 200-day moving average (orange lines) on the 1D chart. Now, I know what you're thing, TA is bullshit, Muh quad witching. I know, so lets see what happened the past 10 time this happened. Ill refer to the death cross as DC from here on out.\n\n&#x200B;\n\n**1.** **6 december 2018**\n\nAfter an intial plunge from SPX 2941 to 2604, DC appeared 2 days AFTER the second recovery to the 2800 zone, SPX at 2600-2700 range at moment of appearance. Aftermath:  SPX nosedove to 2340 18 days later with only a single green day in between.\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/lv4icj7g8zp41.png?width=1170&format=png&auto=webp&s=f31442bc8f050bc0c1799b484941a02b45ccedf0\n\n**2. 6 januari 2016**\n\nDuring a still shaky market closely after DC no 3 (see image below), spy plunged from 2080 to 1920 in just 7 trading days before the DC appeared. After DC market fell further to 1815 over 10 trading days with no significant recovery. After this bottom, market rebounded to 1940 10 days later, retested the bottom another 10 days later, before recovering entirely by mid-april.\n\n&#x200B;\n\n**3. 28 august 2015**\n\nMarket plunged from 2100 to 1870 in just 4 trading days. DC appeared on the top of the recovery to 1990 4 days later. Market retested the bottom 1 month later but did not drop lower.\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/vd3seqbk8zp41.png?width=1313&format=png&auto=webp&s=8ddab1008d2309e65512574e2121122cd700dac4\n\n**4. 11 august 2011**\n\nMarket plunged from 1350 to 1100 over the course of 15 trading days. DC appeared on a recovery day to 1170. Aftermath: market retested low 3 times, bottoming out at 1070 2 months later.\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/6kndd7159zp41.png?width=1044&format=png&auto=webp&s=171a76ccc1c76c5c5d28bcecbf255aaff6a62504\n\n**5. 2 juli 2010**\n\nThe bulls will love this one. Market went down from 1220 to 1020 over 2.5 months before appearance of the DC. Aftermath: it was the bottom, although after a rebound to 1130, a low of 1040 was retested\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/zqyrbbqm9zp41.png?width=915&format=png&auto=webp&s=5a6629af51c7f7954ad7fc6f37268d8ed5e9d29f\n\n**6. THE BIG ONE, 20 december 2007 (yes you read that right, 2007! not 2008)**\n\nThe market entered a period of shaky trading in late 2007, with a top SPX of 1575 on 10 october 2007. 2 months before and after this top, a dip to 1400 was recrded and the DC appeared at an apparent rebound period at SPX 1485. Aftermath: bear market for more than a year, bottom at 660 in march of 2009.\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/sb841y3cazp41.png?width=1156&format=png&auto=webp&s=0e60a26bdb7ecffc94e97c462e78f2cdb0c6ee43\n\n**7. 19 juli 2006**\n\nMarket dropped from 1325 to 1220. DC appeared at first retest of this bottom. Aftermath: It was almost exactly the bottom, almost straight line recovery from there on out.\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/igyd62dqazp41.png?width=815&format=png&auto=webp&s=9886fc4e69cbd603e4c916942d14ee9151c454c3\n\n**8. 17 august 2004**\n\nmarket drop from 1140 to 1060 over 1.5 months after a volatile (but essentially flat) trading year. DC appeared during the beginning of the first real recovery. Aftermath: Lows were not retested.\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/vhurcuu2bzp41.png?width=1445&format=png&auto=webp&s=4f079745aaac893b84a0a36649598b934b0e9599\n\n**9. ANOTHER BIG ONE, 27 october 2000**\n\nSPX dropped from 1530 on september 30 to 1300 on october 18. DC appeared on recovery period at 1390. Aftermath: Huge drop over 2 years to bottom out at 770.\n\n&#x200B;\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/rwyx6jsibzp41.png?width=1016&format=png&auto=webp&s=75a06da3cfa7b262c58925cae20656d1363c8e81\n\n**10. 29 september 1998**\n\nmarket topped on 20 juli at 1190 and dropped to 940 on september 1. DC appeared on the top of the recovery to 1070. Aftermath: bottom on october 8, a little below the previous bottom at 920.\n\n&#x200B;\n\nhttps://preview.redd.it/bpszbbrndzp41.png?width=986&format=png&auto=webp&s=2ea2ed7662a1ed3faf07acf660d4dafa15569cfd", "created_utc": 1585648346.0, "permalink": "/r/wallstreetbets/comments/fsa5t6/a_wild_death_cross_just_appeared_analysis_of_the/", "is_self": true}